{"word":"G2048 - ἔρημος - érēmos - er'-ay-mos - Desert","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἔρημος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>érēmos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>er'-ay-mos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Desert"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"பாழான, அநாதையான, வனாந்தரமான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. solitary, lonely, desolate, uninhabited"},{"paragraph":"2. a desert, wilderness"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Of uncertain affinity; <i>lonesome</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>waste</i> (usually as a noun, <a href=\"#/G5561 - χώρα - chṓra - kho'-rah/5561\">G5561</a> being implied): - desert, desolate, solitary, wilderness."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2047 - ἐρημία - erēmía - er-ay-mee'-ah/2047\">G2047</a>, <a href=\"#/G2048 - ἔρημος - érēmos - er'-ay-mos/2048\">G2048</a>, <a href=\"#/G2049 - ἐρημόω - erēmóō - er-ay-mo'-o/2049\">G2049</a>, <a href=\"#/G2050 - ἐρήμωσις - erḗmōsis - er-ay'-mo-sis/2050\">G2050</a>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}